== Introduction ==
The [http://www.ecotainer.org/ EcoBox] is a self-contained environmentally [[sustainable]] workshop built from a standard '''shipping container'''. The workshop should comfortably accommodate 2 people for extended periods, and include all [[energy]] needs and [[waste disposal]] without connections to outside systems, excepting sunshine and rain.

